    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You inflict despair on creatures in the area. The effects for each creature are determined by its Will save.</p>\r<p>\n<hr><b>Critical Success</b>  The creature is unaffected.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Success</b>  For 1 round, the creature can't use reactions and must attempt another save at the start of its turn; on a failure, it is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed} 1 for that turn as it sobs uncontrollably.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Failure</b>  For 1 round, the creature can't use reactions and must attempt another save at the start of its turn; on a failure, it is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed} 1 for that turn as it sobs uncontrollably.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Critical Failure</b>  As failure, and the creature is automatically @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed} 1 for 1 minute.</p>\r<p>\n<hr><b>Heightened (7th)</b>  The area increases to a 60-foot cone.</p>",
